reviewText: Shipped Fast and just as advertised! Wonderful!!
Looking forward to starting to put this info into practice.

I liked the content, I just wish there was more.  It seems like the author just gets us started with what we need to know and leaves us wanting more.  It would be more helpful to have more on each DVD.
Meredith Hodges is one of the more  knowledgeable people when it comes to training & working with  mules & donkeys
